name: com.android.phone.vvm.RemoteVvmTaskManager
description: Service to manage tasks issued to the VisualVoicemailService. This service will bind to the default dialer on a visual voicemail event if it implements the VisualVoicemailService. The service will hold all resource for the VisualVoicemailService until VisualVoicemailService.VisualVoicemailTask#finish() has been called on all issued tasks. If the service is already running it will be reused for new events. The service will stop itself after all events are handled.
